  id: 87
  title: The Observer
  author: Friedrich Schiller
  isFemaleAuthor: 0
  stanzas:
  - lines:
    - Stern as my conscience, thou seest the points wherein I'm deficient;
    - Therefore I've always loved thee, as my own conscience I've loved.
  rating: 0
